(3647, 'widget_testimonials_widget', 'a:3:{i:2;a:2:{s:5:"title";s:32:"What lawyers are saying about us";s:8:"textarea";s:1305:"<div class=''testimonilas-item''>\r\n            <em>As a securities lawyers and sensitive to the need to maintain orderly books and records of any company, I am a big believer in the business proposition of KoreConX.  </em>\r\n            <p>Douglas Ellenoff   |  Partner<br/>Ellenoff Grossman & Schole LLP</p>\r\n        </div>\r\n        <div class=''testimonilas-item''>\r\n            <em>As a lawyer who deals with all forms of commercial litigation including director and officer liability, KoreConX will dramatically assist in obtaining and maintaining critically important information for clients. Oscar is a leader in the field and has delivered a suite of products that will take managing corporate governance into the 21st century.</em>\r\n            <p>Chris MacLoed  |  Partner<br/>Cambridge LLP</p>\r\n        </div>\r\n        <div class=''testimonilas-item''>\r\n            <em>KoreConX is a fantastic tool for keeping track of corporate actions and making sure you get it right</em>\r\n            <p>Bonnie Rae  |  Partner<br/>Cohen &  Gresser LLP</p>\r\n        </div>\r\n        <div class=''testimonilas-item''>\r\n            <em>You have a very clean and well thought-out solution</em>\r\n            <p>O’Brien, Esq  |  General Counsel & VP Strategy</p>\r\n            <p>Brightleaf Corporation</p>\r\n        </div>";}i:3;a:2:{s:5:"title";s:31:"What people are saying about us";s:8:"textarea";s:1454:"<div class=''testimonilas-item''>\r\n            <em>Working as an independent, free-lance firm that provides Corporate Secretarial services to organizations, CHRISTINET Consulting Inc. is able to effectively administer and distribute any vital information through the KoreConX.  KoreConX has given us a single point of access in managing our client’s informational needs.  We are able to reference confidential documents, and key contact info all within an easy to navigate environment, while ensuring that the best governance practices are being fulfilled.  KoreConX provides us with the complete solution for board information management</em>\r\n            <p>Christina Wilton<br/>CHRISTINET Consulting Inc </p>\r\n        </div>\r\n        <div class=''testimonilas-item last''>\r\n            <em>I have set up KoreConX for my client and have found it to be amazing. Well done! I’m so happy using it and my Board Chair wonders how we did without it </em>\r\n            <p>Natasha Golinsky | Certified Expert </p>\r\n        </div>\r\n<div class="center">\r\n<img class="img-responsive" src="http://koreconx.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/koreconx-certified-expert-logo.png"/>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="fee">\r\n<h1>Set-up fee<span class="number">$595.00 US</span></h1>\r\n<em>Includes listing within the KoreConX platform\r\nKoreConX Training and Certification (One individual)</em>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="fee">\r\n<h1>Annual fee<span class="number">$195.00 US</span></h1>\r\n</div>";}s:12:"_multiwidget";i:1;}', 'yes'),
