(805, 4, '2015-07-24 23:35:12', '2015-07-24 23:35:12', '<strong>KoreConX Latest News and Articles:</strong>\n\n<strong>News Releases </strong>\n\n<strong>22 July 2015</strong>\nKoreConX Included in DealIndex Alternative Finance Report\n<a href="http://www.marketwired.com/press-release/koreconx-included-in-dealindex-alternative-finance-report-2040818.htm" target="_blank">http://www.marketwired.com/press-release/koreconx-included-in-dealindex-alternative-finance-report-2040818.htm</a>\n\n<strong>10 July 2015</strong>\nEquity Crowdfunding at LatAM Start-up Conference\n<a href="http://www.marketwired.com/press-release/equity-crowdfunding-at-latam-startup-conference-2037419.htm" target="_blank">http://www.marketwired.com/press-release/equity-crowdfunding-at-latam-startup-conference-2037419.htm</a>\n\n<strong>16 June 2015</strong>\nEquity Crowdfunding 101 Canadian Tour\n<a href="http://www.marketwired.com/press-release/equity-crowdfunding-101-canadian-tour-2030274.htm" target="_blank">http://www.marketwired.com/press-release/equity-crowdfunding-101-canadian-tour-2030274.htm</a>\n\n&nbsp;\n\n<strong>ARTICLES</strong>\n\n22 July 2015\n\nIndustry Report Disruptive Finance is Making Finance More Transparent Efficient Democratic for Entreprenuers Investors\n\nhttp://www.crowdfundinsider.com/2015/07/71611-industry-report-disruptive-finance-is-making-finance-more-transparent-efficient-democratic-for-entrepreneurs-investors/\n\n&nbsp;\n\n<strong>27 May 2015</strong>\nWe know Equity Crowdfunding -But What is Pre-Crowd?\n<a href="http://www.equities.com/editors-desk/crowd-investing/crowdfunding/we-know-equity-crowdfunding-but-what-is-pre-crowd" target="_blank">http://www.equities.com/editors-desk/crowd-investing/crowdfunding/we-know-equity-crowdfunding-but-what-is-pre-crowd</a>\n\n<strong>07 April 2015</strong>\nTime for Provincial Regulators to Step up, Canada needs enhanced crowdfunding Regulations to match US regulation A+\n<a href="http://www.equities.com/editors-desk/crowd-investing/crowdfunding/time-for-provincial-regulators-to-step-up-canada-needs-enhanced-crowdfunding-regulations-to-match-u-s-regulation-a" target="_blank">http://www.equities.com/editors-desk/crowd-investing/crowdfunding/time-for-provincial-regulators-to-step-up-canada-needs-enhanced-crowdfunding-regulations-to-match-u-s-regulation-a</a>\n\n<strong>31 March 2015</strong>\n6 Opportunities in Equity Crowdfunding\n<a href="http://www.equities.com/editors-desk/crowd-investing/crowdfunding/6-equity-crowdfunding-opportunities-for-investors-and-consumers" target="_blank">http://www.equities.com/editors-desk/crowd-investing/crowdfunding/6-equity-crowdfunding-opportunities-for-investors-and-consumers</a>\n\n<strong>02 March 2015</strong>\nInterview: KoreConX’s Oscar Jofre on Why Equity Crowdfunding Will Still be the Biggest Thing in the World\n<a href="http://www.equities.com/editors-desk/crowd-investing/crowdfunding/interview-koreconx-oscar-jofre-equity-crowdfunding-still-biggest-thing-world" target="_blank">http://www.equities.com/editors-desk/crowd-investing/crowdfunding/interview-koreconx-oscar-jofre-equity-crowdfunding-still-biggest-thing-world</a>\n\n<strong>03 December 2014</strong>\nCrowdfunding? 7 Steps to help you prepare for a successful US campaign\n<a href="http://business.financialpost.com/entrepreneur/crowdfunding-7-steps-to-help-you-prepare-for-a-successful-u-s-campaign" target="_blank">http://business.financialpost.com/entrepreneur/crowdfunding-7-steps-to-help-you-prepare-for-a-successful-u-s-campaign</a>\n\n<strong>31 October 2014</strong>\nEquity Crowdfunding is changing Venture Capitalism in Canada\n<a href="http://www.huffingtonpost.ca/shannon-m-nelson/crowdfunding-small-business_b_6079302.html" target="_blank">http://www.huffingtonpost.ca/shannon-m-nelson/crowdfunding-small-business_b_6079302.html</a>', 'KoreConX News', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'closed', '', '75-autosave-v1', '', '', '2015-07-24 23:35:12', '2015-07-24 23:35:12', '', 75, 'http://koreconx.com/